reviews.review_text: Best Source for This Great Show Stellar show, huge energy... Amazed this particular recording doesn't have any reviews yet. For a show with only AUD sources, I believe this one has the best mix, clarity, and dynamic range. Great job to the taper! Look no further... Better download this one for the collection.
